ganga/python/GangaPanda
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* New Jedi backend:
  - Usage is very similar to Panda backend but without splitter !
  - Example:
    j.backend=Jedi()
    j.backend.nobuild=True
    j.backend.requirements.disableAutoRetry=True
  - No DQ2JobSplitter is needed since the splitting is done autmatically on the server
  - The new backend is not yet enable in the athena command line script
* Upgrade to DQ2Clients 2.5.0
* Upgrade to panda-clients 0.5.0-jedi
* Added protection for slc5 64bit Athena use (uuidgen problem)


